<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TKT3">
<l>pāyirum paravai taṉṉuḷ paruvarai tirittu vāṉōrk</l>
<l>kāyirun tamutaṅ koṇṭa vappaṉai yempi rāṉai</l>
<l>vēyiruñ cōlai cūḻntu virikati ririya niṉṟa</l>
<l>māyiruñ cōlai mēya maintaṉai vaṇaṅki ṉēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I bowed to our Lord [and] Father who is beautiful</l>
<l>And who got nectar for the celestials, spinning a great mountain in the spreading dark sea,</l>
<l>The warrior who dwells in the dark, vast grove that stood [thick]</l>
<l>So that the spreading [sun]rays retreated being surrounded by vast groves of bamboo.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
